Package: VEMCODataMgmt
Type: Package
Title: Functions for Making VEMCO Data Management Smoother and More Efficient
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Brian", "Moe", , "brian.moe@MYfwc.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Allows for greater organization of newly downloaded VEMCO detection data for further use. Allows for easily 
  pulling specific detection data (by date or transmitter ID) out of a larger database or subdirectory folders. Some basic functions for 
  manipulating and combining VEMCO detection data.
